    <content:encoded><![CDATA[あるAnonymous Coward 曰く、<blockquote><div><p>CEOの報酬が多い企業ほど、その業績は悪いという話があるそうだ（<a href="http://gigazine.net/news/20140708-highest-paid-ceo-worst-performer/">GIGAZINE</a>、<a href="http://www.forbes.com/sites/susanadams/2014/06/16/the-highest-paid-ceos-are-the-worst-performers-new-study-says/">Forbes</a>）。
